<docs>
	<doc for="ISqlParameter">
		<summary>
			<para>Allows an object to create a relational data parameter to 
      a command, and its mapping to <see cref="System.Data.DataSet"/> columns.</para>
		</summary>
		<remarks>
			<para>The <see cref="System.Data.ISqlParameter"/> interface inherits from the <see cref="System.Data.IDataParameter"/> 
interface and allows a .NET data provider to create a data
parameter for use with a SQL Server relational database. </para>
		</remarks>
	</doc></docs>
